{"tid":2241004,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"｜消息：患者到過蘋果IFC店　蘋果公司：按當局指引停業","createTime":"2020-10-13T04:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T02:49:45.000Z","uid":5195,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"80ef349e494f8e7a0ecd40ca07616debd05cae27","tid":2241004,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T04:57:11.000Z","msg":"有消息指，有確診新型肺炎的患者曾到訪蘋果公司 IFC分店，蘋果公司網頁顯示，IFC分店今日及明日會停業。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果公司回覆《香港01》查詢時，未有回應該患者是分店的職員還是顧客，亦無披露患者到訪日期，僅稱一直把顧客和團隊的健康和安全放在首位，確保在安全，健康的環境下，商店才會營業。蘋果公司指，出於謹慎考慮並按照衞生防護中心指引，暫時關閉了蘋果公司 IFC商店，期待在不久後重新開業。<br />\n<br />\n而衞生防護中心的患者行蹤名單上，則未見有患者報稱於過往14日到過IFC商場的蘋果分店，僅有一人、第5102號個案於IFC商場的餐廳「無二」任廚師。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba595f1b42be56ea55b7448730bef5ce96ae44ed","tid":2241004,"uid":22556,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T04:58:21.000Z","msg":"如果係iPhone 12 出售果日 應該好精彩"},{"pid":"5b2aca2ae59bc24c021876785545e27a867bab90","tid":2241004,"uid":212623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T04:59:08.000Z","msg":"Booom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2584cd91667224311f1fd47c5618646f792703","tid":2241004,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T04:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a50927ab36681cce573da3b066e374999b69bd37","tid":2241004,"uid":74171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ba595f1b42be56ea55b7448730bef5ce96ae44ed","tid":2241004,"uid":22556,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T04:58:21.000Z","msg":"如果係iPhone 12 出售果